article:
This is a listing of the 'United States Senators from [[Delaware]]'. They were
originally elected by the Delaware General Assembly for designated six-year
terms beginning March 4. Frequently portions of the term would remain only upon
a senator's death or resignation. From 1914 the senators were popularly elected
on the first Tuesday after November 1, and starting 1935 the beginning of their
term is January 3, not March 4.
categories: Lists of United States Senators by state|Delaware
